01:00:54.000 --> 01:01:18.000
Or vice versa, what will be the responsibility for the implementation of a research project, which is expensive, and most importantly, prestigious, from a prestigious customer, if you do not have enough human resources, or you are limited by time limits, or you do not have enough technical resources to implement it?

01:01:18.000 --> 01:01:41.000
