01:02:36.000 --> 01:02:56.000
It is necessary to encode each questionnaire and each answer, each question, in order to see disagreements or limit the incorrect filling of these questionnaires, identify, select those questionnaires that were incorrectly filled,

01:02:56.000 --> 01:03:12.000
enter the data of the answers of these questionnaires into the computer program, conduct processing and analysis of these data using various methods of analysis, and, in the end, prepare the report and presentation.

