01:03:56.000 --> 01:04:16.000
then it is quite possible that you will face some objections or even disapproval of the conclusions and results of your research, because employees of your organization often look at third-party consultants or researchers.

01:04:16.000 --> 01:04:41.000
How can this be overcome? First of all, you need to be sure that the quality, representative and valid information collected in this report is the basis.

01:04:41.000 --> 01:04:58.000
And most importantly, you need to know the results of this research very well and report on them in detail. Or describe it all in a written report on the research.

