01:05:40.000 --> 01:06:00.000
274 surveys were collected, a large number of such studies. The research project was carried out immediately after the completion of the advertising campaign, which the manufacturer paid for and placed on the first two central channels of Moscow Central Television.

01:06:00.000 --> 01:06:23.000
Respondents were invited to conduct research from the street near the Mayakovskaya subway station, to the cinema in the Khanzhonkov house, to demonstrate them again, and then determine the preferences, loyalty, knowledge of the brands of mayonnaise that are on the Moscow market.

01:06:23.000 --> 01:06:47.000
