External secondary data is not published for the purpose of a specific research, for example, the research of similar developing markets in order to identify trends.

01:32:45.000 --> 01:32:55.000
And also the specially organized collection and analysis of primary data that is carried out within the framework of a research project.

01:32:55.000 --> 01:33:01.000
In its general form, Kotler proposes to define the marketing information system as follows.

01:33:01.000 --> 01:33:15.000
A set of components or components interconnected with each other, designed to collect, store, process data and distribute information necessary for making decisions, ensuring control and coordination of the company's marketing activities.

01:33:16.000 --> 01:33:29.000
If we talk about the developers of corporate information systems that have marketing data or marketing information systems in their blocks,

01:33:29.000 --> 01:33:49.000
there are already enough of them in the Russian market, both domestic and foreign developers, first of all Microsoft Business Solutions, or Navision, or some other companies that are developers of software.

01:33:50.000 --> 01:34:03.000
Among domestic developers, I would like to highlight the company Kurs, which has developed a special information database that can be easily adapted into corporate information systems.

01:34:03.000 --> 01:34:18.000
It is called Marketing Analytics. In its general form, this information system allows to implement various types of projects from the point of view of internal and external data analysis,

01:34:18.000 --> 01:34:37.000
such as direction for portfolio analysis, segmentation analysis of consumers, creation and management of marketing databases, regardless of the market of the company, consumer or corporate customers,

01:34:37.000 --> 01:34:50.000
whether they are engaged in the production of goods or services. In any case, this system is well integrated into the general corporate management system of the company.
